abstract: >-
  A contamination-resistant synthetic benchmark for agentic-RAG / memory systems.
  Eleven headline metrics (conversion, chain-fragility, distraction, fact-retention-at-budget,
  outcome-ranked recall, forget-precision, echo-resistance, compression-vs-raw, operational-continuity,
  temporal-as-of, integrity-conditioned-recall) with pre-registered falsifiers, bootstrap confidence intervals, a
  frozen sha256-pinned dataset, a single runner, a number-verification ledger, a reusable Folklore
  Meter probe, and a four-gate preflight that refuses inadmissible comparisons.
